{"tid":1608722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實家下好多速龍已經唔係真速龍來","createTime":"2019-10-01T11:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T13:25:14.000Z","uid":64922,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cc55fbd4c30fe11aa116cab1857b502c3329e4a9","tid":1608722,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:33:35.000Z","msg":"真速龍基本都係得咁多<br />\n睇各區情況真實唔會有咁多<br />\n依Ｄ訓練唔係話1~2個月就train出來<br />\n武警公安扮又未必可行，始終公安對地理地形唔熟好易賴野<br />\n好懷疑有d根本換件速龍裝就扮出來<br />\n示威者潛意識就對速龍恐懼感<br />\n只要普通防暴雜popo<br />\n換多幾百件速龍裝佢地好有效就做倒更大震攝效果<br />\n不過雖然有機係會速龍裝防暴雜popo，你又唔會知佢地佈防邊Ｄ放真放假"},{"pid":"1fa8b9866fa902ddd2c4333a178c69d6f2b4d952","tid":1608722,"uid":241628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:35:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6118bb8a7097bfdc7a7e561e1d5f534647acde3d","tid":1608722,"uid":321593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:40:34.000Z","msg":"速龍？取晒gear隻抽呀笨"},{"pid":"91fc7ef6b86a561129441c7f6234f2639ea712a6","tid":1608722,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"我都覺 邊有咁多速龍 每區出動"},{"pid":"c71225ee93eee543593b8efc5ffc939b46a2e362","tid":1608722,"uid":138092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"班速龍一早已經係畜牲武警扮喇"},{"pid":"4238dabb9bdf67bd39eb8eb7717e1358edc8ef99","tid":1608722,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"係唔係真其實無咩大分別"},{"pid":"92c09013920b7d247406eca4e15cdcb8f9799e0f","tid":1608722,"uid":245644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"而家連中學生都憤怒到要上街了"},{"pid":"44e7f73e981834487b56493efa68d1e5cbc2b91c","tid":1608722,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4238dabb9bdf67bd39eb8eb7717e1358edc8ef99","tid":1608722,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"係唔係真其實無咩大分別"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2